{
  "texts": [
    "c Cumulative power (lines), power distribution (bars), autocorrelation function (ACF), and total power relative to healthy subjects (histogram) for the patient (red) and mean of controls (blue) functional signals of the regions in the DMN.",
    "Error bars [mean ± SEM] indicate the results for the control population, while \"*\" codes for statistical significance.",
    "The relative power was obtained by averaging over subjects and DMN regions and taking healthy subjects as the baseline (i.e., equal to 1).",
    "d Functional DMN from the same patient and mean of control subjects (see Methods).",
    "e Functional complexity as measured by the distribution of correlations for the patient's network (red) and the mean of control (blue) [mean ± SEM] (see Methods)."
  ]
